<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM10.1">
<l>kārkkōṭaṟ pūkkāḷ kārkkaṭal vaṇṇaṉeṉ mēlummaip</l>
<l>pōrkkōlañ ceytu pōra viṭuttava ṉeṅkuṟṟāṉ</l>
<l>ārkkō viṉinām pūca liṭuva taṇituḻāyt</l>
<l>tārkkōṭu neñcan taṉṉaip paṭaikkaval lēṉantō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O brown-backed mangrove flowers! Where is the black ocean-hued [Lord]</l>
<l>Who dressed you up in martial array and sent [you] to me?</l>
<l>Who shall we complain to now? I am able to have a heart</l>
<l>that runs after [His] beautiful tulsi garland, alas!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
